{{Top|canon=Synth-fur}}
'''Synthfur''' was a type of material. The collar of a coat worn by [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] [[Roan Shryne]] had a collar made of synthfur.<ref name="darklord">''[[Dark Lord: The Rise of Darth Vader]]''</ref> [[Zehrinne Thaal]] had a wrap of synthfur that she wore around her shoulders.<ref name="mercykill">''[[X-Wing: Mercy Kill]]''</ref>

